{
  "stem": "26983.8",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Their job was to take out the golden tooth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they smuggled in gold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, they knew they were-- I know exactly when they were executed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See, and I asked--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they always changed and they would say, uprising in October '44 in the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't successful.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But a few people survived, which were staying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all which were trying to run away were shot, killed, or caught and killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, nobody as far as I-- from Auschwitz running away, yes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were a few prisoners who run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even there are famous cases of two prisoners who later on gave a report to--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even to the Pope and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was difficult to believe what's going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Vrba, I think, was one name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And anyhow, so these people come in, and told me exactly what was his job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told me the first job was he had to burn his own parents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean they took them away, and the first time they opened the gas chamber, it was his parents, his transport.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he didn't want to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he wanted to hang himself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the safe team had to give him a different job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came to be a kind of a sewing with the sewing machine to do [INAUDIBLE] repair.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But his job was holding people at single executions, when they were shooting them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he told me, when people were full of unrest or so, he had to hold them on the ear, that they shouldn't move too strongly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the SS man shoots him here in the neck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If they were not willing to go calmly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later on I asked him about all the details.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
